Marvel Comics Presents v2 (001 - 012) (2007 - 2008) (Digital) (AnPymGold-Empire) 


Marvel Comics Presents Volume 2 
 
A revival of the long running Marvel Comics Presents vol.1 series. Like it's predecessor it contained short stories told in continuing chapters featuring Marvel's hottest characters and creators. This second volume lasted 12 issues and was replaced by the second volume of  Astonishing Tales
